Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.accordion

Class AccordionServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<AccordionComponentType,Accordion>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.accordion.AccordionServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
AccordionService
public class AccordionServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<AccordionComponentType,Accordion> implements AccordionService
Default implementation of AccordionService that delegates accordion actions to a cached or newly created Accordion instance.

This class extends AbstractComponentService, enabling the framework to maintain and reuse accordion implementations across multiple test interactions. Each method resolves the appropriate AccordionComponentType to retrieve the correct implementation, then calls the matching methods on the retrieved Accordion.

Typical usage involves specifying which accordion component type to interact with (e.g., different Material Design or Bootstrap variants), and then calling methods like expand(), collapse(), or getExpanded() to operate on those panels.
